laura wissert left us a 5 star review for our Garland location.
See what they have to say about us.
"From beginning to end, the purchasing of my vehicle from Drive Casa was an ease. Mr. Moreno made the process smooth and efficient. I applied online and soon after I received a text stating I was approved. The next step was providing all the necessary documents prior to arriving. The very next day, I went in to test drive the car I had my eye on. Needless to say, I drove off with a classy luxury car. They made me one happy customer. I highly recommend them and Mr. Moreno!

I almost forgot to mention, I have a recent repo and an out of state driver's license. I was so surprise they were able to make a deal with me without eye gauging monthly payments. This is a place of 2nd, 3rd etc. chances."

."
